entry.summary:
We report recent progress in calculating semileptonic form factors for the $ ar{B} 	o D^\ast \ell  ar{
u}$ and $ ar{B} 	o D \ell  ar{
u}$ decays using the Oktay-Kronfeld (OK) action for bottom and charm quarks. We use the second order in heavy quark effective power counting $\mathcal{O}(\lambda^2)$ improved currents in this work. The HISQ action is used for the light spectator quarks. We analyzed four $2+1+1$-flavor MILC HISQ ensembles with $a\approx 0.09\,\mathrm{fm}$, $0.12\,\mathrm{fm}$ and $M_\pi \approx 220\,\mathrm{MeV}$, $310\,\mathrm{MeV}$: $a09m220$, $a09m310$, $a12m220$, $a12m310$. Preliminary results for $B	o D^\ast\ell
u$ decays form factor $h_{A_1}(w)$ at zero recoil ($w=1$) are reported. Preliminary results for $B 	o D\,\ell
u$ decays form factors $h_\pm(w)$ over a kinematic range $1<w<1.3$ are reported as well.
